title: Gerald Kein Hypnosis For Attention Deficit Disorder
description:
Gain the necessary knowledge to work successfully with your clients
with A.D.D. even when others may have failed!
According to experts, the established model for treatment of Attention Deficit Disorder has proven to be marginally successful.
The hypnotherapist understands that the conscious mind and chemical therapies are unable to effect the necessary rapid change for the individual labeled with this behavior problem.
By working with the organic computer of the clients subconscious mind, using relatively basic hypnotic and transformational techniques, we discovered that this problem can often be quickly eliminated!
